<div class="hero-unit">
  <h1>Warning!</h1>
  <p>The actions bellow are permanent and cannot be recovered, ask your administrator before running any of the bellow actions.</p>
  <p>
    <a class="btn btn-primary btn-large">
      Send a request mail
    </a>
  </p>
</div>
<div class="well">
<table class="table table-striped table-bordered table-condensed">
  <thead>
